arts.ttl: Pep Biel has goal, two assists to propel Charlotte to 4-1 victory over Earthquakes
arts.sum: Charlotte led 3-0 at the half after Brandt Bronico used an assist from Biel in the 40th minute to score for the first time this season and the sixth time in his career. Pep Biel had a goal and two assists to propel Charlotte FC to a 4-1 victory over the San Jose Earthquakes at Bank of America Stadium on Saturday night.
